steps.name: Given  User is logged on to LMS website
And  User clicks on "A New Batch" button
And  User is on Batch details page pop-up box
When  User enters "Tech Explorer2" in text box "Batch Name"
And  User enters "Python" in text box "Description"
And  User selects "Inactive" using radio button
And  User enters "20" in text box "No of classes"
Then  User gets a message "Batch created"
And  Records of the newly created "Tech Explorer2" is displayed
